{"tid":1471820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幾條撚樣就搞到咁","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T16:26:02.000Z","uid":119084,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b585f5803cd77bf7af92a8459fe000b34b0c09","tid":1471820,"uid":119084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"我希望大家唔好咁進激住，快手睇埋先<br />\n<br />\n首先我支持五大訴求，但港獨我係絕對唔認同，而且只會令更多人對我哋反感，你堅持得一國兩制嘅同時，點可以自打嘴巴講港獨？<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔該唔好亂打人dllm，咪撚同我講咩唔割蓆唔分化，依家個問題係合理同唔合理，就算疑似公安真係影手足大頭/疑似跟蹤，最多咪同佢對質/叫佢del相，有咩可能打人先，仲有上緊救護車途中你都仲要打多搥，你係咪男人啊？呢幾條撚樣真係無資格話自己係和理非，話自己係香港人dllm<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣只係俾人分化，覺得我哋先係錯嗰班，大家勿忘初心，我哋本意係想大家好香港好，香港人都會支持，但係大家一失民意就死得啦"},{"pid":"3d180dd8b4716c50faf1f9afd7dff53dfbbc5c33","tid":1471820,"uid":202889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"手足以後捉到鬼，一律咁樣招呼佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8PFqPe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8PFqPe.jpg&h=6f9e94ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ff4976ff19226209fa7b02e4e378e1af6f6bc2b","tid":1471820,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25d9dcfc4881342b65e307542e5554ee39b36b0f","tid":1471820,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019